java projclu arg1 [arg...] text-files
-a     = consider apostrophes in *grams
                Do not use without -g option.
                Do not use with -u option.
-c     = give a-z character frequency
                If used with -u, gives all characters
-g x y = give top y x-grams
-s     = consider spaces in *grams
                Do not use without -g option.
                Do not use with -u option.
-w     = give word count
                Does not consider punctuation.
-u     = parse files in unicode
                Do not use with -s or -a options.
